1. *Istoj* godini je završila univerzitet. (She finished university the same year.)
2. Ona je *istoj* boji kose kao i ja. (She has the same hair color as me.)
3. *Istoj* večeri smo se sreli u gradu. (We met in the city that same evening.)
4. Njihov odnos se nije promenio ni u *istoj* meri. (Their relationship hasn't changed in the same degree.)
5. Oni su se zabavljali u *istoj* kafani. (They were having fun in the same cafe.)